{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room/task-44","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Ako želiš da saznaš o karakteru ili ličnosti osobe, možeš pitati, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">What is (he/she) like?</span> ili <span class=\"highlighted-text\">What are they like?</span>. Ova pitanja su o osobnim karakteristikama, a ne o njenom spoljašnjem izgledu.</p>\n<p>Na primer, zamisli da naiđeš novog studenta u svoj programski razred i želiš da saznaš više o njemu/njoj. Možeš pitati svog drugog iz klase <span class=\"highlighted-text\">What is she like?</span></p>\n<p>Ne znate da li taj učenik voli računare ili igre; pitate ga o njegovom karakteru. Možda je prijatelj, pametan ili stručnjak za programiranje.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"English","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room/task-44"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Izaberite odgovarajuće pitanje koje treba da postavite o karakteru i navikama Marije.</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">What does she like?</span></p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">What does she like?</span> Koristi se za pitala o nečijim preferencijama.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">What is she like?</span></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">What does she look like?</span></p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">What does she look like?</span> je pitanje o izgledu osobe, a ne o njenoj ličnosti.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">What she is like?</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Redos reči nije tačan; druga reč u pitanju treba da bude pomoćni glagol <span class=\"highlighted-text\">is</span>.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":2}],"scene":null,"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","tests":[],"title":"Vežba 44","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/#learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room","dashedName":"task-44","certification":"a2-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room/task-45","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room/task-43","id":"657cb5dd956a8797462da793","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":22,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room/task-44"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}